query:
UPDATE users
                    SET
                        first_name = $2,
                        last_name = $3,
                        email = LOWER($4),
                        phone = $5,
                        password = $6,
                        password_reset_token = $7,
                        verification_token = $8,
                        last_logged_in_at = $9,
                        current_logged_in_at = $10,
                        updated_at = NOW(),
                        deleted_at = $11
                    WHERE id = $1
